ect and the galactic winds as a dominant\ninfluence on the CGM's angular momentum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Apr 2020 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 May 2020 19:04:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-22"}
