if the individuals avoid social\ninteractions in order to not spread a disease, this leads the system to have a\nfinite threshold in scale-free graphs, allowing for epidemic control.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 00:01:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-26"}
