lows for simple stability and performance analysis of the\nclosed-loop in presence of disturbances. A particular application to\nlarge-scale systems with actuator saturation and safety constraints is\npresented in our companion paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 00:13:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-20"}
