omising candidate for daily re-contouring in\nadaptive radiotherapy, potentially reducing treatment-related side effects and\nimproving quality-of-life after treatment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 08:55:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-20"}
