eeting their deadlines. We conduct\nreal extensive experiments on NVIDIA GPUs using several benchmark applications.\nThe experiment results have shown that our prediction models have high accuracy\nwith the average RMSE values of 0.38 and 0.05 for energy and time prediction,\nrespectively. Also, the scheduling algorithm consumes 15.07% less energy as\ncompared to the baseline policies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 11:21:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Apr 2020 01:47:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-29"}
