stic ontologies\nand compared the obtained proofs with proofs generated by the DL reasoner ELK,\nfinding that forgetting-based proofs are often better w.r.t. different measures\nof proof complexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2020 15:44:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2020 13:53:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-29"}
